# Project Language

- All project artifacts are written in English: source code, comments, commit messages, documentation, glossary/ADRs, and the CLI's user-facing output.
- Chat conversation may be in any language; this rule governs committed artifacts and shipped output, not the conversation.
- i18n is out of scope — English is the single base language.
